Package org.sedml.validation

Interface Summary
ISedMLValidator Interface for different sorts of validation that can be performed on a SED-ML model or file.
 

Class Summary
CrossReferenceValidator Class that checks all mandatory cross-references of IDs between elements.
KisaoIDValidator  
MultipleIdentifierValidator Class which validates whether multiple elements have the same ID.
All identifiable elements should have a unique ID in a SED-ML document.
SEDMLSchemaValidator Class responsible for validating a SED-ML file against its XML schema.
SemanticValidationManager Main point of access for validating the model outside of the schema.
